import { useState } from "react"

export const Myform=(props)=>{
   const [itemf,setitemf ]=useState({})
   return<>
    <form>
        <input placeholder="enter name" onChange={(e)=>setitemf({...itemf,name:e.target.value})}></input>
        <input placeholder="enter color"  onChange={(e)=>setitemf({...itemf,color:e.target.value})}></input>
        <input type='submit' onClick={(ev)=>props.onadd()}></input>
    </form>
    </>

}
